{"task":"transcribe","language":"english","duration":30.0,"text":"in the prehistoric northern southwest. Although research is beginning to disclose the existence of regional systems that existed at other times and other places in the Puebloan area, the Chicoan system reached a level of hierarchy, complexity, and costliness that exceeded all others. The demarcating attribute of the Chicoan system is its architecture. Two generalized kinds of Chicoan structures have been characterized by archeologists. The first, called great houses, Chicoan structures, or towns.","segments":[{"id":0,"seek":0,"start":0.0,"end":2.119999885559082,"text":" in the prehistoric northern southwest.","tokens":[50364,294,264,659,33236,16345,14197,34363,13,50508],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2313012331724167,"compression_ratio":1.7725632190704346,"no_speech_prob":0.17083711922168732},{"id":1,"seek":0,"start":3.140000104904175,"end":5.059999942779541,"text":" Although research is beginning to disclose the existence","tokens":[50508,5780,2132,307,2863,281,36146,264,9123,50620],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2313012331724167,"compression_ratio":1.7725632190704346,"no_speech_prob":0.17083711922168732},{"id":2,"seek":0,"start":5.059999942779541,"end":7.519999980926514,"text":" of regional systems that existed at other times","tokens":[50620,295,10964,3652,300,13135,412,661,1413,50744],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2313012331724167,"compression_ratio":1.7725632190704346,"no_speech_prob":0.17083711922168732},{"id":3,"seek":0,"start":7.519999980926514,"end":9.760000228881836,"text":" and other places in the Puebloan area,","tokens":[50744,293,661,3190,294,264,430,622,15962,282,1859,11,50880],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2313012331724167,"compression_ratio":1.7725632190704346,"no_speech_prob":0.17083711922168732},{"id":4,"seek":0,"start":10.399999618530273,"end":12.5,"text":" the Chicoan system reached a level of hierarchy,","tokens":[50880,264,761,2789,282,1185,6488,257,1496,295,22